page.title: 10URBAN WEST CORNFORTH II
page.content:
quiet. The Church(C.of.E) stands at the top over looks the rest.Most of the houses are over 100 years old and have been modernised.
The rest of the village is mainly council and O.A.P.'s houses, except for a few private houses along the main bus route.The O.A.P.'s houses are all very modern except for some old ones built befor the First World War.Every house has a bell to be souned if the old people aren't very well,A warden is always on duty within a few minutes walk of the houses.
